00:20:44.199 --> 00:20:56.160
It is wholly dependent on us to find the method of communication that results in a person understanding.

00:20:56.160 --> 00:20:58.359
That is key.

00:20:58.359 --> 00:21:02.699
And if you'd say, you know what, you're just gonna have to trust me on this, and you have

00:21:02.699 --> 00:21:09.459
built a relationship with the decision makers where that is a thing that they can accept,

00:21:09.459 --> 00:21:13.699
you do whatever modeling you need to do in order to get to the end state, and then next

00:21:13.699 --> 00:21:14.900
you'd be, yeah, go for it, right?

00:21:14.900 --> 00:21:17.300
Go for it because it's going to work, and you can prove that it's going to work.

00:21:17.300 --> 00:21:24.819
